INSTRUCTIONS
-Create a folder called new_files. Location of new_files folder should be the same as that for main_file.py
-Rename the excel file to be analysed to stem_statement.xlsx
-run main_file.py on the terminal
-navigate to new_files
-run subsidiary_file.py
-Once these files run successfully then we have our statements ready.
-To repeat this process, replace the earlier stem statement with the one you want to analyze
-Also delete the earlier generated individual's excel files in the new_files folder.  
